{"type": "article", "id": 28600, "title": "室内菜园", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-23T06:51:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121035HJGVxXwo4W8E2prD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>并不是所有人都能拥有一个户外小菜园，对于想要“自给自足”的烹饪爱好者来说，室内菜园可以省去不少麻烦。4Senses 公司研发的 Calla 就是这么一款智能的桌上水耕菜园，模块型的设计最多可以种植六种不同的植物，中央还留有空间可以加入养料。除此之外，Calla 内置的 LED 灯会模仿太阳光，确保你可以轻松地照料好这些植物。这是它的众筹<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/940126036/calla-fresh-herbs-indoor-garden-0\">链接</a>，早鸟价为 95 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121031ofBZiEmwgdFl097j.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121031QXEf5NaKW7RZicMs.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66125\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121033wQ4CM05UyTE7vZD1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121033tv67cW8ErbkAoIUp.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}